rs, and allies of the order must come together once again and protect the good people of the west from the horrors of the east.The Bolts & Brawlers Mercenary Co.  have been sent an invitation to help in this oncoming battle.History:Battle of the Vorstuga River - Teutonic State Part I", "link_list": ["http://thefantasysandbox.boards.net/thread/1535/vorstuga?page=1&scrollTo=33221", "/user/1170", "http://thefantasysandbox.boards.net/thread/897/battle-vorstuga-river-teutonic-state"], "image_list": ["https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/f1/5a/41/f15a41a470eed044a5bbde9ec38a0b35.jpg"], "html": "<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/f1/5a/41/f15a41a470eed044a5bbde9ec38a0b35.jpg\" height=\"428\" src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/736x/f1/5a/41/f15a41a470eed044a5bbde9ec38a0b35.jpg\" width=\"607\"/><br/></div>"}, "post-33219": {"user": "Silas", "user_num": 139, "timestamp": "1460678098000", "message": "Silas and Oliver will both fight for the Brotherhood this time.", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "Silas and Oliver will both fight for the Brotherhood this time."}, "post-33222": {"user": "The Kingdom of Audria", "user_num": 491, "timestamp": "1460678521000", "message": "Sounds good. Actually got the Vorstuga thread up in the Lost Worlds category, and am waiting for someone to move it back to the boards.", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "Sounds good. Actually got the Vorstuga thread up in the Lost Worlds category, and am waiting for someone to move it back to the boards."}, "post-33447": {"user": "[Phoenix] Zaltos Kiraxo", "user_num": 29, "timestamp": "1460846592000", "message": "I want in. Giplor would have made sure there was a strong naval presence on the river.", "link_list": [], "image_list": [], "html": "I want in. Giplor would have made sure there was a strong naval presence on the river."}, "post-33452": {"user": "King Konrad I von Audria", "user_num": 484, "timestamp": "1460848791000", "message":